		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
		
		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="+2">Kilijs Plans</FONT><BR>
Zone : Greater Faydark<BR><BR>
<TABLE CELLSPACING = 0 CELLPADDING = 0 BORDER = 0>
<TR><TD>On the same platform as the druid guildhall is a weapon shop.  Outside the shop
is a npc that if you hail him will tell you about Kilij's plans.  If you bring him the plans and three
enchanted gold bars, he will make a weapon.  The plans come from a sand giant in So Ro.  He's
not named but he is in the twenties instead of the thirties like most sand giants. Get an
enchanter to enchant three gold bars and give the npc the bars, don't stack them, and the
plans, and in return you receive the <A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/weapon_detail.php3?search=282">Brazen Brass Kilij</A>.  (Submitted by Gzaz Taintedtouch)<BR><BR></TD></TR>
</TABLE>
